Pre-Game Insights: Experts favored Egypt to win based on their history against Congo DR
Rui Vitoria's side have only lost one of their five Africa Cup of Nations encounters against Congo DR while winning three and drawing the other
Others: The fourth match in the round of 16 at the Africa Cup of Nations will see Egypt take on Congo DR at Stade Laurent Pokou on Sunday evening.
The winner of this match will move on to the quarter-final, where they will face either Equatorial Guinea or Guinea, who square off earlier in the day in Abidjan.
